name: PCcooler Halo FX-120 Dynamic Color Case Fan
desc: This Case Fan has a maximum speed of 1400 RPM. It comes with 4-Pin PMW. It delivers a maximum airflow of 45.18CFM and has a static pressure of 2.15mmH2O. It features 8~26.5dB(A) noise level. It has Hydraulic Bearing. The PCcooler Halo FX-120 comes with no warranty.

name: AMD Ryzen 3 4100 Processor
desc: It has 4 processor cores, 8 threads, and an astonishingly efficient 45-65W TDP. This processor stands with a Base Clock of 3.8GHz and a Maximum Boost Clock of 4.0GHz. It has 256KB L1 Cache. 2MB L2 Cache, 4MB L3 Cache with AM4 Package, and TSMC 7nm FinFET CMOS. This AMD processor is built with PCIe 3.0 x8 and Wraith Spire Thermal Solution and provides DDR4 Up to 3200MHz memory with 2 memory channels.

name: Gigabyte H310M H Motherboard
desc: This 8-Channel HD Audio with High Quality Audio Capacitor board has dual channel DDR4 maximum 32GB memory and it has the capability of Ultra-Fast SATA 6Gb/s connectors and USB 3.1 Gen 1 interface. If we consider the graphics of this Anti-Sulfur Resistors Design board supports Intel HD graphics having the maximum resolution of 4096x2160@30 Hz for HDMI and 1920x1200@60 Hz for D-Sub port.

name: PNY CS900 120GB SATA III Internal SSD
desc: This is the ideal solution for a mainstream solid state drive (SSD) upgrade from a hard disk drive (HDD). The CS900 delivers all the most sought after features at an excellent value, and is designed for an easy and cost-effective HDD replacement in the PC system to help realize faster boot times, quicker application launches and better overall system performance.

name: Western Digital 1TB Purple Surveillance HDD
desc: It is developed specifically for surveillance security systems. It offers us reduced video frame loss. Tuned for write-intensive, low bit-rate, high stream-count applications typical to most surveillance applications. Moreover, it prioritizes write-operations for maximized surveillance performance.

name: Apacer Panther RAM
desc: It has a high level of compatibility. It is backward compatible with Intel and AMD series systems. This pattern is in the shape of a claw.

name: Gigabyte Graphics Card
desc: Full HD widescreen video calling: Logitech C270 let you make widescreen video calls in HD 720p at 30fps. The lense with 60-degree field of view covers all of the action

name: Xtreme V3 Gaming Case
desc: This Gaming Case's Country Of Origin is China, and it is made in China. This Xtreme V3 Case is a Full Window type Gaming Case. This Gaming case supports Micro-ATX motherboards. It is designed with ABS injection & a Black metal net in the front panel. It has 2 Red Pre- Installed Cooling Fans.
